{"tid":1316484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求警方給予新城市內的香港人好市民獎","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:44.000Z","uid":266172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d78d0cea9daf7d0c2255fd79c1201fc24ab2b4b","tid":1316484,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"制服暴徒，人人有責。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/03_police_message/gca.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F03_police_message%2Fgca.html&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=eff70992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/03_police_message/gca.html</a><br />\n<br />\n獲提名角逐好市民獎的人士必須具備以下條件：<br />\n    獲提名人士不論是案中目擊證人或受害人，<span style=\"color: red;\">必須曾積極協助警方或其他市民防止或偵查罪案，或逮捕罪犯</span>；以及<br />\n    獲提名人士所提供的協助，必須是重要及有實際作用的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全年好市民獎</span><br />\n全年好市民獎的提名標準基本上與好市民獎相同，但獲提名人士必須曾顯出：<br />\n    <span style=\"color: red;\">特別英勇的行為或勇氣；<br />\n    高度的機智；或<br />\n    非凡的積極性。</span><br />\n<br />\n排隊去拿獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}